ivers and forests should be prioritized over preventing arable land expansion.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Akasaka, Takumi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Akasaka, Munemitsu", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Nakamura, Futoshi", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/cfa7e920026617acdfa57fe1cfceedd4", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/a6f3abfdc70e7a1cd20631cb15baaa484f08021674a517ad56740a14c3c1d414", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/KRKPECYR", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/KRKPECYR", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/a71448c75f3071f9dba7d05aad0d48a3!/b312165-314726", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "15-23", "title": "Biological Conservation", "volume": "145"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/cfa7e920026617acdfa57fe1cfceedd4"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:KRKPECYR"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.biocon.2011.08.017"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "14821348"}}]}}, "title": "Scale-independent significance of river and riparian z